Package: nuts
Title: 'nuts': Convert European Regional Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Moritz", "Hennicke", , "AAoritz@posteo.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6811-1821")),
    person("Werner", "Krause", , "werner.krause@uni-potsdam.de", role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5069-7964"))
  )
Description: Motivated by changing administrative boundaries over time,
    the 'nuts' package can convert European regional data with NUTS codes
    between versions (2006, 2010, 2013, 2016 and 2021) and levels (NUTS 1,
    NUTS 2 and NUTS 3). The package uses spatial interpolation based on
    granular (100mx100m) population and land use data provided by the
    European Commission's Joint Research Center.
